    "7787429": {
      "title": "The existence of solutions for the system of vector quasi-equilibrium problems in topological order spaces",
      "abstract": "Abstract This paper introduces two kinds of quasiconcave mappings which are different from the usual quasiconcave function. We establish a result for the existence of solutions for the system of vector quasi-equilibrium problems in the frame of topological order, by providing a maximal elements version of the well known Browder fixed points theorem."
